modShortDescription: Vehicle Mods modlet. Enables the Vehicle mods the Fun Pimps have in-game. Adds them to loot and to traders.
modDescription:
Vehicle Mods modlet. Enables the Vehicle mods the Fun Pimps have in-game. Adds them to loot and to traders. Surprisingly AnsontheToad hasn’t seen anyone else do this yet it was one of the first things he modded for A19\. He’s sure a bunch of others did too. Added to traders and in loot.

**[Download](https://docs.google.com/uc?export=download&id=1W1ZNt2wiOV0StCsGERamykgu3ShvufGH)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/20895-toads-modlets/).

**Credits:** [AnsontheToad](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/ansonthetoad/)
